<main role="main">
  <section class="jumbotron text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="jumbotron-heading">The Pattern Place</h1>
        <p class="lead">Store, organise and learn with your community, all in one place!</p>
        <p>It's time to ditch the printed instructions, the disorganisation and the wasted storage space. Interactive instructions are here to improve your space and sewing experience.</p>
